lead_paragraph: In a video interview with Kurdish TV, Marilyn Nevalainen, 16, said she knew nothing about the Islamic State before she ran away to Iraq with her boyfriend.

headline.main: Swedish Girl Who Ran Away to Iraq Says She Had Not Heard of ISIS
